ygData.messageBody:
"So what's in the lake in the West Commons anyway? Can you zone
to/fromthe
Ocean Of Tears? Who needs a stinky boat - I'm swimming from Freeport to
Butcherblock!"

---------

I know what you're saying. I can't wait for this song myself. I am
dying ot jump through the holes in the ice in the frozen river in
Everfrost. But, alas, you cannot zone thorugh Ocean of Tears without
being on a boat. Can't even zone if you are on the little canoes.

You learn things from falling off of the boat.
